WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
The agreement to build NYU Abu Dhabi is based on the shared 

00:03.000 --> 00:06.000
understanding of the crucial role of higher education and a shared commitment 

00:06.000 --> 00:09.000
to educating students who are citizens of the world, prepared to lead 

00:09.000 --> 00:13.000
at home and contribute to global trade, politics, and culture. 

